---
import MainLayout from "@/layouts/MainLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "Disclaimer | WinFlowz";
---

<MainLayout
  title={pageTitle}
  lang="en"
  structuredData={{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    "@id": "https://winflowz.com/disclaimer",
    "url": "https://winflowz.com/disclaimer",
    "name": "Disclaimer | WinFlowz",
    "description": "Legal disclaimer and limitation of liability for WinFlowz digital productivity tools and services.",
    "inLanguage": "en"
  }}
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">Disclaimer</h1>

    <p class="text-sm mb-4 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">Last updated: December 15, 2024</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">1. General Information</h2>
      <p>
        The information provided by WinFlowz ("we," "us," or "our") on our website and through our products is for general informational purposes only. All information is provided in good faith, however, we make no representation or warranty of any kind, express or implied, regarding the accuracy, adequacy, validity, reliability, availability, or completeness of any information.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">2. No Guaranteed Results</h2>
      <p>
        While we strive to provide accurate and useful information about productivity and digital tools:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Results from using our products may vary based on individual circumstances</li>
        <li>Productivity gains mentioned in marketing materials are examples and not guaranteed outcomes</li>
        <li>Time-saving estimates are based on average user experiences and may differ for each user</li>
        <li>Success stories and testimonials represent individual experiences and not typical results</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">3. Technical Limitations</h2>
      <p>Users acknowledge that:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Software may contain bugs or technical limitations despite thorough testing</li>
        <li>Compatibility with third-party services depends on their respective APIs and may change</li>
        <li>Performance may vary based on hardware, internet connection, and system configuration</li>
        <li>Updates to Obsidian or browsers may temporarily affect plugin functionality</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">4. Professional Advice</h2>
      <p>
        Our products and services do not constitute professional advice. Users should:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Not rely solely on our tools for critical business or personal decisions</li>
        <li>Seek appropriate professional advice for specific situations</li>
        <li>Use their own judgment when implementing productivity strategies</li>
        <li>Verify any information or suggestions provided through our services</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">5. Third-Party Content</h2>
      <p>Regarding external content and services:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>We are not responsible for third-party content accessed through our tools</li>
        <li>Links to external websites are provided for convenience only</li>
        <li>We do not endorse or verify third-party content</li>
        <li>Users access external content at their own risk</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        Under no circumstances shall WinFlowz be liable for any indirect, incidental, consequential, special, or exemplary damages arising from:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Use or inability to use our products</li>
        <li>Data loss or business interruption</li>
        <li>Errors or omissions in our content</li>
        <li>Security breaches or technical issues</li>
        <li>Any other matter relating to our services</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        Under no circumstances shall WinFlowz be liable for any indirect, incidental, consequential, special, or exemplary damages arising from:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Your use or inability to use our products</li>
        <li>Loss of data or profits</li>
        <li>System failures or interruptions</li>
        <li>Any errors or omissions in our content</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">8. Changes and Errors</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Modify or discontinue any part of our services without notice</li>
        <li>Correct any errors or omissions in any content</li>
        <li>Change the terms of service at any time</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="mt-8">
        By using our products and services, you expressly agree to these disclaimer terms. If you disagree with any part of this disclaimer, please do not use our services.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">
      For any questions about this disclaimer, please contact legal@winflowz.com
    </p>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
